The article is a statement by the President of the United States regarding the announcement made by the Office of the Prosecutor for the Special Tribunal for Lebanon about filing an indictment for the assassination of former Prime Minister Rafiq Hariri and 22 others. The President welcomes this announcement as an important step towards ending impunity for murder in Lebanon and achieving justice for the Lebanese people. The statement emphasizes the need for calm and restraint from all Lebanese leaders and factions during this emotional time. The United States expresses its support for Lebanese sovereignty, independence, and stability, and emphasizes the importance of allowing the Special Tribunal for Lebanon to continue its work without interference or coercion. The President also condemns any attempts to fuel tensions and instability, as they undermine the freedom and aspirations of the Lebanese people. The statement concludes by calling on all friends of Lebanon to stand with the people of Lebanon at this critical moment.